## 13. KEY DIFFERENCES: IRC VS NOSTR

| Aspect | IRC | Nostr |
|--------|-----|-------|
| **Account Model** | Host/port/nick (scoped) | Single privateKey (top-level) |
| **Chat Types** | direct + group | direct only |
| **Media Support** | Yes (as URL in text) | No (MVP) |
| **Text Limit** | 350 chars | 4000 chars |
| **Connection** | Persistent TCP/IRC client | Relay-based event bus |
| **Pairing** | nick-based (with `!user@host`) | pubkey-based (hex/npub) |
| **DM Policy** | pairing/allowlist/open/disabled | pairing/allowlist/open/disabled |

